#!/usr/bin/env bash
# hooks/session-start — Workflow skills bootstrap hook
# Outputs skill awareness text for injection into the session context.

set -euo pipefail

cat <<'BOOTSTRAP'
## Workflow Skills Available (workflow-skills v5.0.0)

Use /workflow:<skill> to invoke. Each phase requires explicit user approval before proceeding.

### Skills

| Command | Trigger |
|---------|---------|
| /workflow:init | Project setup, scaffold docs structure |
| /workflow:research | Background research, competitive analysis |
| /workflow:brainstorm | New feature idea, problem framing, scope classification |
| /workflow:discovery | Complex feature domain requirements (COMPREHENSIVE scope) |
| /workflow:prd | Formal product requirements (after brainstorm/discovery) |
| /workflow:technical-design | Architecture, API specs, data models (after PRD) |
| /workflow:plan | Implementation plan, task decomposition (after design) |
| /workflow:beads | Work packages with FR traceability (after plan) |
| /workflow:execute | Implement from approved beads |
| /workflow:review | Parallel agent code review (after implementation) |
| /workflow:review-prd | Adversarial PRD quality review |
| /workflow:review-design | Adversarial design review against PRD/ADRs |
| /workflow:review-plan | Adversarial plan review against authority sources |
| /workflow:review-beads | Adversarial bead compliance review |
| /workflow:review-execute | Post-execution bead satisfaction verification |
| /workflow:compound | Capture learnings by phase/domain (after review) |
| /workflow:diagnose | Bug investigation, root cause analysis |
| /workflow:qa | Browser-based QA testing, diff-aware |
| /workflow:benchmark | Performance benchmarking, regression detection |
| /workflow:security-audit | OWASP + STRIDE zero-noise audit |
| /workflow:ship | Release pipeline: changelog, PR, traceability |

### Pipeline (scope-based routing)

BRIEF (0-2 pts):         brainstorm -> plan -> beads -> execute -> review -> ship
STANDARD (3-4 pts):      brainstorm -> prd -> technical-design -> plan -> beads -> execute -> review -> ship
COMPREHENSIVE (5+ pts):  brainstorm -> discovery -> prd -> technical-design -> plan -> beads -> execute -> review -> ship
Bug fix:                 diagnose -> fix / beads / brainstorm

### Rules
- Never write implementation code until user explicitly approves
- All phases produce documentation under docs/
- Requires br (beads-rust) CLI for task management
BOOTSTRAP
